						<summary>

						<p>On another slab set up in a street of the village.</p>						

						<p>Eastern Chāḷukya: Sarvalōkāśraya Vishṇuvardhana, 37th year.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of lands to the Śānta-Jinēśvarālaya at Munugōḍu by <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Goṁkaya. In characters of the 11th century A.D.</p>						

